  "detailed_description": "Bold is a unique, quiet and elegant third person exploration game, as well as a Zen game for traveling, walking, watching picturesque landscapes.<br />\r\nThe protagonist of the game, deer (bold), finds deer herds and obtains inner peace by crossing grasslands, deep forests, wilderness, rivers, and lakes.<br />\r\nKey Features:<br />\r\nAn independent and moving warm story produced by a single person team has unforgettable scenery.<br />\r\nWith a melodious soundtrack, the melody is soothing.<br />\r\nA short game at the heart of the landscape.<br />\r\nAt this moment of global economic downturn, I hope players can gain peace of mind and regain the courage of life through this game.<br />\r\nPEACE.LOVE",
  "about_the_game": "Bold is a unique, quiet and elegant third person exploration game, as well as a Zen game for traveling, walking, watching picturesque landscapes.<br />\r\nThe protagonist of the game, deer (bold), finds deer herds and obtains inner peace by crossing grasslands, deep forests, wilderness, rivers, and lakes.<br />\r\nKey Features:<br />\r\nAn independent and moving warm story produced by a single person team has unforgettable scenery.<br />\r\nWith a melodious soundtrack, the melody is soothing.<br />\r\nA short game at the heart of the landscape.<br />\r\nAt this moment of global economic downturn, I hope players can gain peace of mind and regain the courage of life through this game.<br />\r\nPEACE.LOVE",
